description.en:
"The Babelfish project is a brand reboot of the Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy, a once popular SciFi radio series and book anthology originally broadcast and published in the late 1970s. It is a place for lovers of Douglas Adams' masterpiece ""trilogy"" to hang out and share a joke and a drink in a uniquely thematic environment. It is also the biggest meme token slash NFT project to hit the ERC20. Ever. Welcome.
"
